interpretation: The "family: woman, woman, boy" card represents the importance of relationships and the support we receive from our loved ones. This card suggests a strong bond between two women and a young boy, possibly indicating a close-knit family or chosen family. The presence of the child could also represent the need for nurturing and protection. This card encourages you to focus on the relationships that bring you joy and comfort. It reminds you to cherish and appreciate those who love and support you unconditionally.
